<p>Mais c''est quoi un blog ? D''o&ugrave; &ccedil;a vient, comment ce truc est arriv&eacute; jusqu''en 2012 ?</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://4h18.com/histoire-du-blog-un-vent-de-liberte/">Histoire du blog, un vent de libert&eacute;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://4h18.com/">4h18</a>.</p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"L''écho des plugins WordPress : Frontend Uploader";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:55:"http://www.echodesplugins.fr/plugins/frontend-uploader/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:55:"http://www.echodesplugins.fr/plugins/frontend-uploader/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2012-12-01T23:00:00+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"anonymous";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2339:"<div>\n<h2>Vos visiteurs peuvent importer des fichiers dans la biblioth&egrave;que de m&eacute;dias</h2>\n<p><strong><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/frontend-uploader/">Frontend Uploader</a></strong> n&rsquo;est pas un plugin incontournable mais pourra peut-&ecirc;tre rendre service &agrave; quelques uns. Il affiche dans une page/billet des champs pour permettre aux visiteurs d&rsquo;importer des fichiers dans la biblioth&egrave;que de m&eacute;dias. Ces fichiers apparaissent dans un menu &agrave; part et vous pouvez les attacher &agrave; un billet/une page. Un peu plus pratique qu&rsquo;un plugin de contact puisque vous pouvez g&eacute;rer imm&eacute;diatement ces fichiers pour votre contenu. Vous pouvez demander &agrave; &ecirc;tre pr&eacute;venu par mail &agrave; chaque <span class="classtoolTips15" style="border-bottom:2px dotted #888;">upload</span>.</p>\n<h3>Options</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.echodesplugins.fr/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/front-end-upload01.png"><img src="http://www.echodesplugins.fr/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/front-end-upload01-300x166.png" alt="" title="front-end-upload01" width="300" height="166" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-6454 colorbox-6351"></a></p>\n<h3>Rendu visuel</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.echodesplugins.fr/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/front-end-upload02.png"><img src="http://www.echodesplugins.fr/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/front-end-upload02-300x234.png" alt="" title="front-end-upload02" width="300" height="234" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-6455 colorbox-6351"></a></p>\n<h3>Gestion des fichiers</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.echodesplugins.fr/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/front-end-upload03.png"><img src="http://www.echodesplugins.fr/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/front-end-upload03-300x94.png" alt="" title="front-end-upload03" width="300" height="94" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-6457 colorbox-6351"></a></p>\n<span class="notice">- site du plugin: <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/frontend-uploader/">http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/frontend-uploader/</a><br>\n- compatibilit&eacute; &agrave; ce jour: WP 3.2 &gt; WP 3.5.beta1 <br>\n- version test&eacute;e: 0.2.5<br></span>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"WordPress Francophone : WordPress 3.5 Release Candidate 2";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/HcjonZDbnJg/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/HcjonZDbnJg/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2012-12-01T00:16:58+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"anonymous";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3796:"<div>\n<p>Voici l&rsquo;adaptation en fran&ccedil;ais de<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/news/2012/11/wordpress-3-5-release-candidate-2/"> l&rsquo;article d&rsquo;annonce original</a> :</p>\n<p style="padding-left:30px;">La deuxi&egrave;me version candidate pour WordPress 3.5 a &eacute;t&eacute; mise en ligne hier soir et est &agrave; pr&eacute;sent disponible en t&eacute;l&eacute;chargement.</p>\n<p style="padding-left:30px;">Il reste encore une douzaine de correctifs &agrave; apporter mais la version d&eacute;finitive devrait malgr&eacute; tout pouvoir &ecirc;tre livr&eacute; pour la semaine prochaine. Si vous voulez savoir quoi tester dans cett version, consultez la page &laquo;&nbsp;&agrave; propos&nbsp;&raquo; dans la barre d&rsquo;outils (<strong><img src="http://wordpress.org/wp-content/themes/twentyten/images/wordpress.png" alt="">&nbsp;&rarr; A propos</strong>) Comme la version pr&eacute;c&eacute;dente, il s&rsquo;agit d&rsquo;une application de d&eacute;veloppement et l&rsquo;installation en direct n&rsquo;est pas recommand&eacute;e.</p>\n<p style="padding-left:30px;"><strong>Vous pensez avoir d&eacute;couvert un bug,</strong> dites sur le forum anglais, dans cette rubrique<strong> : </strong><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta/">Alpha/Beta area in the support forums</a>.</p>\n<p style="padding-left:30px;"><strong>D&eacute;veloppeurs,</strong> poursuivez vos efforts de tests des extensions et des th&egrave;mes. S&rsquo;il reste des probl&egrave;mes de compatibilit&eacute;, ils pourront certainement &ecirc;tre corrig&eacute;s dans la version finale. La <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/report/6">liste des probl&egrave;mes connus est ici.</a></p>\n<p style="padding-left:30px;">Pour tester WordPress 3.5, essayez <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/">WordPress Beta Tester</a>. Ou bien <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/wordpress-3.5-RC2.zip">t&eacute;l&eacute;chargez la version candidate n&deg;2 (zip)</a>.</p>\n<p style="padding-left:30px;"><em>&ndash;<br></em><em>Nous sommes tr&egrave;s proche<br></em><em>Demandez l&rsquo;aide d&rsquo;un Ha&iuml;ku<br>\nTestez la RC2</em></p>\n<p>Si vous voulez tester une version en fran&ccedil;ais, <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://fr.wordpress.org/builds/fr_FR/branches/3.5/wordpress-3.5-RC2-fr_FR.zip">voici l&rsquo;archive Zip</a> ! Si vous avez des remarques sur la traduction fran&ccedil;aise, <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://fr.wordpress.org/contact/">&eacute;crivez-nous sur ce formulaire</a> !</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=HcjonZDbnJg:Wpho_OEStAk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=HcjonZDbnJg:Wpho_OEStAk:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=HcjonZDbnJg:Wpho_OEStAk:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=HcjonZDbnJg:Wpho_OEStAk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=HcjonZDbnJg:Wpho_OEStAk:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=HcjonZDbnJg:Wpho_OEStAk:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/HcjonZDbnJg" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n 